Introduction

Nam Yuju is a South Korean-Japanese trainee under Evermore Entertainment. She is a member of the agency's pre-debut girl group, currently known as EVERMORE MUSE.

Nam Yuju mostly gained recognition for her participation in multiple survivals shows, notably on CAP-TEEN in the All U team in 2020, Stars Awakening in 2022, and Mnet's I-LAND2: N/a in 2024. She was sadly eliminated from the three shows, making her unable to debut.

During her participation on I-LAND2: N/a, she was signed with WAKEONE.
